               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Dāwit “Psalter” (fols. 3r-143vb)
 I-1) Mazmura Dāwit “Psalms of
                     David” (fols. 3r-113r)
 I-2)Maḥālǝya nabiyat “The Canticles of the
                     Prophets” (fols. 113v-124v)
 I-3) Maḥālǝya maḥālǝy “Song of Songs” (fols.
                     124v-131r)
 I-4) Wǝddāse Māryām “The Praise of Mary” (fols.
                     132ra-140rb)
 I-5) ʾAnqaṣa bǝrhān “The Gate of Light” (fols.
                     140rb-143vb)
 
 Additio 1.</summary>
